{"_id":"ZWVlMjNiMGFkMjNi","name":"Nezznar the Black Spider","type":"npc","img":"worlds/lost-mine-of-phandelver/characters/037_-_Nezznar_the_Black_Spider/avatar.png","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":9,"proficient":0,"bonuses":{"check":"","save":""},"min":3,"mod":-1,"save":0},"dex":{"value":13,"proficient":0,"bonuses":{"check":"","save":""},"min":3,"mod":1,"save":0},"con":{"value":10,"proficient":0,"bonuses":{"check":"","save":""},"min":3,"mod":0,"save":0},"int":{"value":16,"proficient":1,"bonuses":{"check":"","save":""},"min":3,"mod":3,"save":5},"wis":{"value":14,"proficient":1,"bonuses":{"check":"","save":""},"min":3,"mod":2,"save":4},"cha":{"value":13,"proficient":0,"bonuses":{"check":"","save":""},"min":3,"mod":1,"save":0}},"attributes":{"ac":{"flat":11,"calc":"natural","formula":"14 with mage armor"},"hp":{"value":27,"min":0,"max":27,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":"6d8"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":1,"prof":0,"total":1},"movement":{"burrow":0,"climb":0,"fly":0,"swim":0,"walk":30,"units":"ft","hover":false},"senses":{"darkvision":120,"blindsight":0,"tremorsense":0,"truesight":0,"units":"ft","special":"passive Perception 14"},"spellcasting":"int","prof":2,"spelldc":10,"spellLevel":0,"bar1":{"value":27,"min":0,"max":27},"bar2":{"value":11,"min":0,"max":0}},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<h4>Picture: <span style=\"font-weight: normal\"><a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=JournalEntry data-id=MzI4NGMwNzA5NDY0 ><i class=\"fas fa-book-open\"></i>Handout: Nezznar</a></span></h4><p style=\"font-family: &#34;helvetica neue&#34; , &#34;helvetica&#34; , &#34;arial&#34; , sans-serif\"><br></p><h4 style=\"font-family: &#34;helvetica neue&#34; , &#34;helvetica&#34; , &#34;arial&#34; , sans-serif\">Roleplaying Nezznar</h4><p style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">Even though he intends to kill the characters, Nezznar is curious about them. Given the chance, he quizzes the characters at length regarding their identities, allegiances, interests, and goals. He files it all away in memory in the hope that someday he might find a use for what he learns.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\">Nezznar admits to being the Black Spider, and to using the Cragmaw goblins and the Redbrands to ensure that Wave Echo Cave remains his secret. He will say or do anything to put the characters off their guard, including promising to surrender or proposing cooperation against the monsters impeding his progress toward reaching the Forge of Spells. However, he betrays the characters as soon as they outlive their usefulness.</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb( 64 , 64 , 64 )\"><br></span>Drow (dark elves) are a devious, scheming subterranean race that worships Lolth, the Demon Queen of Spiders. Drow society is strictly matriarchal. Male drow are relegated to servitor roles, and while most train as warriors, a few, such as Nezznar, become skilled wizards.</p><h2>Traits</h2><p><b>Special Equipment.</b> Nezznar has a spider staff.</p><p><b>Fey Ancestry.</b> Nezznar has advantage on saving throws against being charmed, and magic can’t put him to sleep.</p><p><b>Sunlight Sensitivity.</b> Nezznar has disadvantage on attack rolls when he or his target is in sunlight.</p><p><b>Innate Spellcasting.</b> Nezznar can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:</p><ul><li>At will: dancing lights</li><li>1/day each: darkness, faerie fire (save DC 12)</li></ul><p><b>Spellcasting.</b> Nezznar is a 4th-level spellcaster that uses Intelligence as his spellcasting ability (spell save DC 13; +5 to hit with spell attacks). Nezznar has the following spells prepared from the wizard’s spell list:</p><ul><li>Cantrips (at will): mage hand, ray of frost, shocking grasp</li><li>1st Level (4 slots): mage armor, magic missile, shield</li><li>2nd Level (3 slots): invisibility, suggestion</li></ul><h2>Actions</h2><p><b>Spider Staff.</b> Melee Weapon Attack: +1 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 2 (1d6 – 1) bludgeoning damage plus 3 (1d6) poison damage.</p><div><br></div>\n<hr><section class=\"secret\"><p><strong>GM Notes :</strong> </p><h3>Locations</h3><ul><li><a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=JournalEntry data-id=ZjA5MTFiZDk2ZWE4  style=\"background-color: rgb( 255 , 255 , 255 )\"><i class=\"fas fa-book-open\"></i>Keyed Encounters</a>: Area 19<br></li></ul></section>","public":""},"alignment":"Neutral Evil","race":"","type":{"value":"humanoid","subtype":"Elf","swarm":"","custom":""},"environment":"","cr":2,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":450},"source":"Roll 20","class":""},"traits":{"size":"med","di":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dv":{"value":[],"custom":""},"ci":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":["elvish","undercommon"],"custom":""}},"currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0},"skills":{"acr":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""},"bonus":0,"mod":1,"passive":11},"ani":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""},"bonus":0,"mod":2,"passive":12},"arc":{"value":1,"ability":"int","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""},"bonus":0,"mod":5,"passive":15},"ath":{"value":0,"ability":"str","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""},"bonus":0,"mod":-1,"passive":9},"dec":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""},"bonus":0,"mod":1,"passive":11},"his":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""},"bonus":0,"mod":3,"passive":13},"ins":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""},"bonus":0,"mod":2,"passive":12},"itm":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""},"bonus":0,"mod":1,"passive":11},"inv":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""},"bonus":0,"mod":3,"passive":13},"med":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""},"bonus":0,"mod":2,"passive":12},"nat":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""},"bonus":0,"mod":3,"passive":13},"prc":{"value":1,"ability":"wis","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""},"bonus":0,"